Where one stands a chance
against meeting a senseless
death...

29
00:01:59,926 --> 00:02:01,535
That's correct.

30
00:02:01,535 --> 00:02:02,636
Huh?

31
00:02:02,703 --> 00:02:05,038
Are you saying... that from
now on, I'm gonna be able to

32
00:02:05,071 --> 00:02:08,141
just up and fight Kings
like you, Nagare?

33
00:02:08,208 --> 00:02:12,646
That sounds awesome! I can't
wait! The stronger the
opponent, the better it

34
00:02:12,713 --> 00:02:15,148
feels when you beat them!

35
00:02:15,215 --> 00:02:17,751
The birth of a new world...

36
00:02:17,784 --> 00:02:20,554
...where Kings battle
against Kings.

37
00:02:20,587 --> 00:02:23,890
It'll truly be a paradise of
natural selection.

38
00:02:23,890 --> 00:02:28,829
And we're going to be the
