00:04:16,550 --> 00:04:18,885
<i>It almost looks like that</i>
<i>red light we saw before...</i>

44
00:04:18,919 --> 00:04:20,754
[gasping]

45
00:04:20,787 --> 00:04:24,024
This is so weird...Whoa...

46
00:04:29,462 --> 00:04:30,396
